DESCRIPTION
-----------
List::Intersperse - Intersperse / unsort / disperse a list

This module provides functions that evenly distribute elements of a list. 
Elements that are considered equal are spaced as far apart from each other 
as possible.

INSTALLATION
------------
This is a simple module. The typical installation routine should work fine.

  perl Makefile.PL
  make test
  make install

